#. type: Plain text
#: src/chapter_00_introducing_cryptoparty/05_how_to_cryptoparty.md:77
msgid ""
"Let's assume your city does not have a page. Create one for the whole city "
"(e.g. \"https://cryptoparty.in/gotham\"). That's where the information above "
"goes. Locations or parties should have separate sub pages. This allows "
"others to organize parties without having to create a second version of the "
"city page."
